dc_creator_sm: Snohomish County Geographic Information System (GIS), Dept. of Information Services
dc_description_s: This data set shows lines of the Public Land Survey System (PLSS). The grid contains lines demarking Township, Range, Section, and Quarter sections. Lines can be displayed hierarchically (Township being highest) making the framework easier to interpret.
